The folder apk_files all he apk's developed so far on eclipse.
For making an apk you need to install:
a.Eclipse (32 bit if OS is 32 and 64 if OS is 64 bit)
b.ADT plugin for eclipse
c.android sdk
Do not forget to configure proxy settings in both eclipse and sdk for proper installation of packages.
for more help refer:http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html

once installed to make a new project
Eclipse-->New-->Android Project--->Get set go.

